    public class SnomedCrossMapExporter
extends AbstractSnomedCrossMapExporter
    SNOMED CT cross map exporter for complex map and simple map type reference sets.

    RF1 CSV header:

    • MAPSETID MAPCONCEPTID MAPOPTION MAPPRIORITY MAPTARGETID MAPRULE MAPADVICE

    See Also:
